snippet.title: C64 Game - Beyond Dark Castle
snippet.description: I read that this 1989 Activision release sucked because of poor controls, but heck, it isn't that bad when you get used to it! Some great animations, too. I'm showing random parts that I found playing it casually, which include a wizard, a Donkey Kong-esque screen, and a lethal pendulum.
